-- Apple Manager Devine Must Forfeit Proceeds of Alleged Fraud, U.S. Says
-- B y   J o e l   R o s e n b l a t t
-- 2010-11-15T23:00:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/apple-manager-devine-must-forfeit-proceeds-of-alleged-fraud-u-s-says.html
Paul Devine, the Apple Inc. manager
accused of taking kickbacks in exchange for company secrets,
must forfeit proceeds from his fraud, prosecutors said in a
court filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
